When `feedbackKorean` is available and the learner is difficulty 2+, show it below the English feedback. This gives intermediate learners practice reading Korean corrections.

### 6. Cost control

Claude evaluation is only called for scores in the 0.4-0.8 range. In typical sessions:
- ~60% of responses are clear pass (≥0.8) — no API call
- ~20% are clear fail (<0.4) — no API call
- ~20% are ambiguous — API call

For a 20-item session, that's ~4 Claude calls. At ~$0.003 per call (Sonnet, short prompt), cost is ~$0.01 per session.

